Description: Calculates nitrogen fertilization rates following the 
    Emilia-Romagna Regional Recommendation for agricultural crops. The package 
    implements a comprehensive nitrogen balance model that accounts for crop 
    requirements, soil fertility, leaching losses, immobilization, organic 
    fertilization, and natural nitrogen contributions. It includes functions 
    for soil texture classification, NDVI-based nitrogen rate estimation using 
    calibration curves and Holland & Schepers methods, and detailed nitrogen 
    balance calculations for precision agriculture applications.
